# Devalay App Design System Rules

This document defines the design system rules for integrating Figma designs using the Model Context Protocol (MCP) in the Devalay Flutter app.

---

## 1. Token Definitions

### Color Tokens
All colors are defined in `lib/src/presentation/core/utils/colors.dart`:

```dart
// Primary Colors
static const Color orangeColor = Color(0xffFF9500);      // Primary accent
static const Color appbarBgColor = Color(0xffFF9500);    // AppBar background
static const Color appbarBgColor2 = Color(0xffFDF2EE);   // Peach/cream background
static const Color appbarBorderColor2 = Color(0xffFFE0D4); // Peach border

// Background Colors
static const Color whiteColor = Color(0xffFFFDFF);       // Main white
static const Color lightScaffoldColor = Color(0xffFFFDF2); // Light scaffold
static const Color splashBgColor = Color(0xffFFFCEE);    // Splash screen

// Text Colors
static const Color blackColor = Color(0xff111111);       // Primary text
static const Color lightTextColor = Color(0xff494949);   // Secondary text
static const Color subTitleTextColor = Color(0xff555151); // Subtitle text
static const Color greyColor = Color(0xff828282);        // Grey text

// Status Colors
static const Color redColor = Color(0xffF5222D);         // Error/danger
```

### Figma to Flutter Color Mapping
| Figma Variable | Flutter Token |
|----------------|---------------|
| `--primary-text, #241601` | `AppColor.blackColor` or `Color(0xFF241601)` |
| `--background, #fffdff` | `AppColor.whiteColor` |
| `#fee8e0` (selected chip) | `AppColor.appbarBgColor2` |
| `#ffe0d4` (chip border) | `AppColor.appbarBorderColor2` |
| `#12b76a` (success green) | `Color(0xFF12B76A)` |
| `#d9d9d9` (disabled/border) | `Color(0xFFD9D9D9)` |
| `rgba(60,60,67,0.18)` | `Color(0x2E3C3C43)` |
| `#fdf2ee` (error bg) | `Color(0xFFFDF2EE)` |

### Typography Tokens
Defined in `lib/src/presentation/core/utils/theme.dart`:

```dart
// Font Family
fontFamily: 'SF Pro'

// Text Styles (use Theme.of(context).textTheme.*)
headlineLarge:  40sp, weight: normal, color: orangeColor  // AppBar titles
headlineMedium: 24sp, weight: normal                      // Dashboard names
headlineSmall:  20sp, weight: w500, letterSpacing: 1     // Widget titles
bodyLarge:      18sp, weight: w400, letterSpacing: 1     // Bottomsheet titles
bodyMedium:     16sp, weight: normal                      // TextField labels
bodySmall:      14sp, weight: normal                      // General body text
labelLarge:     12sp, weight: w500                        // Labels
labelSmall:     14sp, weight: normal, height: 1.8        // Subtitles
```

### Figma to Flutter Typography Mapping
| Figma Style | Flutter TextTheme |
|-------------|-------------------|
| H3 (18sp, Regular) | `textTheme.bodyLarge` |
| H4 (16sp, Regular) | `textTheme.bodyMedium` |
| H5 body (14sp, Regular) | `textTheme.bodySmall` |
| H6 (12sp, Regular) | `textTheme.labelLarge` |

