## 2. Component Library

### Widget Location
All reusable widgets are in `lib/src/presentation/core/widget/`:

```
widget/
├── custom_button.dart        # Primary button component
├── custom_cache_image.dart   # Cached network images
├── custom_post_card.dart     # Feed post cards
├── feed_appBar.dart          # Main app bar with notifications
├── No_data_found.dart        # Empty state widget
├── bottomsheet.dart          # Standard bottom sheets
├── blurred_dialoge_box.dart  # Blur dialog overlays
└── network_status_widget.dart # Network connectivity indicator
```

### Component Architecture Pattern
```dart
// Stateless widgets for simple UI
class MyWidget extends StatelessWidget {
  final String title;
  final VoidCallback? onTap;
  
  const MyWidget({super.key, required this.title, this.onTap});
  
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    return Container(/* ... */);
  }
}

// Stateful with AutomaticKeepAliveClientMixin for tabs
class MyTabWidget extends StatefulWidget {
  const MyTabWidget({super.key});
  
  @override
  State<MyTabWidget> createState() => _MyTabWidgetState();
}

class _MyTabWidgetState extends State<MyTabWidget> 
    with AutomaticKeepAliveClientMixin {
  @override
  bool get wantKeepAlive => true;
  
  @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    super.build(context);
    return /* ... */;
  }
}
```

