## 3. Frameworks & Libraries

### Core Dependencies
```yaml
# UI & Layout
flutter_screenutil: ^5.9.3    # Responsive sizing (.w, .h, .sp, .r)
gap: ^3.0.1                   # Spacing widget (Gap)
flutter_svg: ^2.0.9           # SVG rendering (SvgPicture.asset)

# State Management
flutter_bloc: ^8.1.6          # BLoC/Cubit pattern
get_it: ^7.7.0                # Dependency injection

# Navigation
go_router: ^14.6.0            # Declarative routing

# Localization
easy_localization: ^3.0.7+1   # Multi-language support

# Images
cached_network_image: ^3.4.1  # Network image caching
```

### Responsive Sizing Pattern
```dart
import 'package:flutter_screenutil/flutter_screenutil.dart';

// Width
16.w  // 16 logical pixels scaled by screen width

// Height
10.h  // 10 logical pixels scaled by screen height

// Font size
14.sp // 14 sp scaled for accessibility

// Border radius
8.r   // 8 radius scaled proportionally
```

