## 4. Asset Management

### Directory Structure
```
assets/
├── background/    # Background images (.png, .jpg)
├── fonts/         # Custom fonts (SF Pro Display)
├── icon/          # Icons (.svg, .png)
├── language/      # Translations (en.json, hi.json)
├── logo/          # App logos and branding
└── music/         # Audio files
```

### Asset Usage Patterns
```dart
// SVG icons
SvgPicture.asset('assets/icon/my_icon.svg')

// PNG images
Image.asset('assets/background/intro_1.png')

// Cached network images
CustomCacheImage(
  imageUrl: url,
  borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8.r),
  width: 90.w,
  height: 90.h,
)
```

