## 5. Icon System

### Icon Storage
All icons are in `assets/icon/` directory.

### Icon Naming Convention
```
{feature}_{state}_{variant}.svg

Examples:
- active_home_icon.svg      # Active state
- dashboard_icon.svg        # Default state
- contribute_active_icon.png # PNG variant
```

### Icon Usage
```dart
// SVG (preferred)
SvgPicture.asset(
  'assets/icon/notification.svg',
  height: 24.h,
  width: 24.w,
  colorFilter: ColorFilter.mode(color, BlendMode.srcIn),
)

// Material Icons (for common icons)
Icon(Icons.check_circle, size: 24.sp, color: AppColor.orangeColor)
```

