## 6. Styling Approach

### Container Styling Pattern (Figma to Flutter)
```dart
// Figma card with border
Container(
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: Colors.white,
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(5.r),    // Figma: rounded-[5px]
    border: Border.all(
      color: const Color(0x2E3C3C43),            // Figma: rgba(60,60,67,0.18)
      width: 1,
    ),
  ),
  padding: EdgeInsets.all(16.w),
  child: /* content */,
)
```

### Button Styling Pattern
```dart
