### Error/Alert Box Pattern
```dart
// Error message box (Already assigned)
Container(
  padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 6.w, vertical: 4.h),
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: const Color(0xFFFDF2EE),      // Light red background
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(5.r),
