## 7. Project Structure

### Clean Architecture Pattern
```
lib/src/
├── application/       # BLoC/Cubit (Business Logic)
│   ├── job/
│   │   ├── job_cubit.dart
│   │   └── job_state.dart
│   └── ...
├── core/              # Core utilities
│   ├── api/           # API calling, constants
│   ├── network/       # Network handling
│   ├── router/        # Navigation
│   └── shared_preference.dart
├── data/              # Data layer
│   ├── model/         # Data models
│   └── repositories/  # API implementations
├── domain/            # Domain layer
│   └── repo_impl/     # Repository interfaces
└── presentation/      # UI layer
    ├── core/          # Shared UI (widgets, theme, colors)
    ├── dashboard/     # Dashboard feature
    ├── feed/          # Feed feature
    └── ...
```

### Feature Organization Pattern
```
feature_name/
├── feature_screen.dart           # Main screen
├── feature_cubit.dart            # State management
├── feature_state.dart            # State definitions
└── widget/                       # Feature-specific widgets
    ├── feature_card.dart
    └── feature_dialog.dart
```

