## 8. Localization

### String Constants
All user-facing strings should use `StringConstant` from `lib/src/presentation/core/constants/strings.dart`:

```dart
// Definition
static String get accept => 'accept'.tr();
static String get reject => 'reject'.tr();
static String get details => 'details'.tr();

// Usage
Text(StringConstant.accept)
```

### Translation Files
Located in `assets/language/`:
- `en.json` - English
- `hi.json` - Hindi

### Adding New Strings
1. Add to `strings.dart`:
   ```dart
   static String get newString => 'new_string'.tr();
   ```
2. Add to `en.json`:
   ```json
   "new_string": "New String"
   ```
3. Add to `hi.json`:
   ```json
   "new_string": "नई स्ट्रिंग"
   ```

