## 9. Figma to Flutter Conversion Checklist

When implementing Figma designs:

- [ ] Extract colors and map to `AppColor` or define new constants
- [ ] Use `flutter_screenutil` for all dimensions (`.w`, `.h`, `.sp`, `.r`)
- [ ] Use `Theme.of(context).textTheme` for typography
- [ ] Create reusable widgets for repeated patterns
- [ ] Use `StringConstant` for all user-facing text
- [ ] Add translations to both `en.json` and `hi.json`
- [ ] Follow existing BLoC/Cubit patterns for state management
- [ ] Match border radius: Figma `5px` → Flutter `5.r`
- [ ] Match padding: Figma `10px` → Flutter `10.w` or `10.h`
- [ ] Use `CustomCacheImage` for network images
- [ ] Use `SvgPicture.asset` for SVG icons

